snippet.textDisplay:
The song is another goosebumps inducing ride.
But the set design takes the lead here. I like how the effect of color exclusion is achieved with actual set pieces. I could watch this video all day to discover new things each time. It's genius.

I think the dancers did an amazing job but they could be shown a bit more. Their shock inducing short presence makes them feel obsolete.
